    <h2>Contribute to the development</h2>
    <p>translate5 project welcomes your contributions to the development on the level you like:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Report bugs</li>
        <li>Propose features</li>
        <li>Fix bugs</li>
        <li>Develop plug-ins</li>
